  "detailed_description": "Your purpose is to eliminate all pixel-based lifeforms by chipping them apart, slicing off sections, and destroying their cores.<br><br>Compete to be fastest on the leaderboards, watch replays from other players to learn their tricks, or team up with a friend in local co-op.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dodge, shoot, and destroy over 14 challenging multi-phase bosses<br></li><li> A variety of powerups - choose offensive or defensive based on your skill level<br></li><li> Leaderboards with a simple scoring system - fastest time wins<br></li><li> Watch replays that you can speed up, slow down, or hijack for practice<br></li><li> Steam Workshop support for custom stages<br></li><li> <strong>NEW</strong>: Local co-op supported for every boss<br></li><li> <strong>NEW</strong>: Easy and Nightmare versions of each campaign</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/602700/extras/29bc916a72faedc70f2254d4c4b94d36.avif?t=1724162553\" width=540 height=221 /></span>",
